title: "The Jack Benny Program" Christmas Shopping Show

sources.title: ChristmasShopping 201512
sources.description: Title: "The Jack Benny Program" Christmas Shopping Show Summary: Jack is determined to finish his Christmas shopping in one visit and tortures a wallet salesman with constant changes to his order. Meanwhile, Dennis is having difficulty finding the right present for his mother. Directed by: James V. Kern Actors: Production Company: J&M Productions Release Date: Episode aired 15 December 1957 Aspect Ratio: 1.33 : 1 Jack is determined to finish his Christmas shopping in one visit and tortures a wallet salesman with constant changes to his order. Meanwhile, Dennis is having difficulty finding the right present for his mother.
